                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d725">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Danish Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Danish Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-05-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 30, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary of State</hi>: With reference to our
                    conversation of yesterday morning I have the honor to inform your excellency
                    that <pb facs="0703" n="537" xml:id="pg_537"/> I am now in possession of a cable
                    message from my Government authorizing me to sign a protocol for the extension
                    of the term mentioned in Article VII of the Convention of January 24 last
                    concerning the Danish West Indies. The telegram does not suggest for how long
                    time said term should be extended, and I therefore conclude that the time
                    proposed by your excellency through the United States Minister at Copenhagen is
                    entirely agreeable to my Government.</p>
                <p>I take pleasure in placing myself at your excellency’s disposal for further
                    agreement on the protocol in question at any time which may be agreeable to your
                    excellency.</p>
                <p>I have [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">C. Brun</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
